attributes.review: First off, when I downloaded this app all my other apps immediately crashed. I tried to open my messages, photos, and even my call log and nothing was working! The only app available was safari so I used it to my advantage to figure out how to get my apps working again. Apparently I had to completely reset my phone which then deleted everything. I can’t even tell you how angry this has made me. Also the app kept giving me a bunch of unrelated advertisements and asking me to pay a $100 subscription yearly. I am highly upset with this app and I absolutely do not recommend it unless you want to lose all of your stuff(including photos/memories).
attributes.title: Not worth it! I lost everything!
